{"tid":1930123,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"德國超越南韓，奪得武漢聯盟第五名","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T12:00:38.000Z","uid":64191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95b087b6a9d38f5a5a3db6631343e6c2ea4099b6","tid":1930123,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M9UEA47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM9UEA47.png&h=d0e6e33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日德國一口氣增加871宗，攀越南韓登上第五位，法包亦緊隨其後，跟住落黎既美帝、瑞士及英國就未構成威脅，預料南韓亦難以重返原位<br />\n<br />\n目前英國、歐盟地區進入閉門練蠱階段，解放後恐怕呈幾何級增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814093be140914bdc8cecf66ecc2ddfb3b37ea87","tid":1930123,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"未完場 始終唔好慶祝住"},{"pid":"738b16376854e3750ff5340f9a0e9dee4621faba","tid":1930123,"uid":24270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"德國想爬頭要問過韓國教會先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e354854bc69c0965b76014d23112efe5ca38595d","tid":1930123,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"德國人，報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebe65eec3acd3610de9c094f725b28d381bdf64","tid":1930123,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"睇好英國，<br />\n今日求其香港已經中幾件倫敦嚟，<br />\n應該個邊過2萬人中左"}]}